## Remarks  
 <span data-ttu-id="7933b-154"><xref:System.Web.XmlSiteMapProvider.BuildSiteMap%2A>呼叫方法來載入和建置網站地圖從永續性儲存體。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7933b-154">The <xref:System.Web.XmlSiteMapProvider.BuildSiteMap%2A> method is called to load and build the site map from persistent storage.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="7933b-155">預設行為時安全性調整已啟用，請參閱 「 備註 」 中<xref:System.Web.SiteMapProvider.IsAccessibleToUser%2A>。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7933b-155">For the default behavior when security trimming is enabled, see "Remarks" in <xref:System.Web.SiteMapProvider.IsAccessibleToUser%2A>.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="7933b-156">在後<xref:System.Web.XmlSiteMapProvider>物件剖析並載入網站導覽資料，所有已載入<xref:System.Web.SiteMapNode>物件和<xref:System.Web.SiteMapNodeCollection>集合會變成唯讀狀態。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7933b-156">After the <xref:System.Web.XmlSiteMapProvider> object parses and loads site map data, all loaded <xref:System.Web.SiteMapNode> objects and <xref:System.Web.SiteMapNodeCollection> collections are made read-only.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="7933b-157">當<xref:System.Web.XmlSiteMapProvider>剖析<xref:System.Web.SiteMapNode.Url%2A>屬性從網站地圖檔案，它會將應用程式相對的 Url，以及相對的 Url，應用程式絕對虛擬路徑。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7933b-157">When the <xref:System.Web.XmlSiteMapProvider> parses the <xref:System.Web.SiteMapNode.Url%2A> property from a site map file, it converts application-relative URLs, as well as relative URLs, to application-absolute virtual paths.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="7933b-158"><xref:System.Web.XmlSiteMapProvider> .Sitemap 檔案的檔案變更通知訂閱。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7933b-158">The <xref:System.Web.XmlSiteMapProvider> subscribes to file change notifications for the .sitemap file.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="7933b-159">如果.sitemap 檔案，進行任何變更<xref:System.Web.XmlSiteMapProvider>重新載入，以及網站導覽結構就會重建。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7933b-159">If any change is made to the .sitemap file, the <xref:System.Web.XmlSiteMapProvider> is reloaded, and the site map structure is rebuilt.</span></span>  
  
   
  
## Examples  
 <span data-ttu-id="7933b-160">下列程式碼範例示範如何建立的新執行個體<xref:System.Web.XmlSiteMapProvider>類別，並將它初始化為建置網站地圖，從 XML 資料。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7933b-160">The following code example demonstrates how to create a new instance of the <xref:System.Web.XmlSiteMapProvider> class and initialize it to build a site map from XML data.</span></span>  
  
```csharp  
<%@ Page Language="c#" %>  
 <!DOCTYPE HTML PUBLIC "-//W3C//DTD HTML 4.0 Transitional//EN">  
 <SCRIPT runat="server">  
 private void Page_Load(object sender, System.EventArgs e)  
 {  
     // Create an instance of the XmlSiteMapProvider class.  
     XmlSiteMapProvider testXmlProvider = new XmlSiteMapProvider();  
     NameValueCollection providerAttributes = new NameValueCollection(1);  
     providerAttributes.Add("siteMapFile","test.sitemap");  
     // Initialize the provider with a provider name and file name.  
     testXmlProvider.Initialize("testProvider", providerAttributes);  
  
     // The BuildSiteMap method is implicitly called when the   
     // RootNode propety is accessed.  
  
     // Prints "/myvirtualdirectory/WebForm1.aspx"  
     Response.Write(testXmlProvider.RootNode.Url + "<BR>");  
     // Prints "/myvirtualdirectory/WebForm2.aspx"  
     Response.Write(testXmlProvider.CurrentNode.Url + "<BR>");  
 }  
```  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="7933b-161">上述程式碼範例會使用位於虛擬根目錄的 ASP.NET 應用程式中的 XML 檔案。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7933b-161">The preceding code example uses an XML file that is located in the virtual root of the ASP.NET application.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="7933b-162">檔案的格式如下：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7933b-162">The file has the following format:</span></span>  
  
```  
<siteMap>  
     <siteMapNode title="RootNode" description="The root page." url="WebForm1.aspx">  
         <siteMapNode title="CurrentNode" description="Some sub page." url="WebForm2.aspx"/>  
     </siteMapNode>  
 </siteMap>  
```

  
  
## Remarks  
 <span data-ttu-id="7933b-250"><xref:System.Web.XmlSiteMapProvider>類別會覆寫繼承<xref:System.Web.XmlSiteMapProvider.Initialize%2A>方法來套用數個屬性，例如`siteMapFile`並`description`屬性，為`attributes`集合。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7933b-250">The <xref:System.Web.XmlSiteMapProvider> class overrides the inherited <xref:System.Web.XmlSiteMapProvider.Initialize%2A> method to apply several attributes, such as the `siteMapFile` and `description` attributes, to the `attributes` collection.</span></span>  
  
   
  
## Examples  
 <span data-ttu-id="7933b-251">下列程式碼範例示範如何建立的新執行個體<xref:System.Web.XmlSiteMapProvider>類別，並將它初始化為建置網站地圖，從 XML 資料。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7933b-251">The following code example demonstrates how to create a new instance of the <xref:System.Web.XmlSiteMapProvider> class and initialize it to build a site map from XML data.</span></span>  
  
```csharp  
<%@ Page Language="c#" %>  
<SCRIPT runat="server">  
 private void Page_Load(object sender, System.EventArgs e) {  
     // Create an instance of the XmlSiteMapProvider class.  
     XmlSiteMapProvider testXmlProvider = new XmlSiteMapProvider();  
     NameValueCollection providerAttributes = new NameValueCollection(1);  
     providerAttributes.Add("siteMapFile","test.sitemap");  
  
     // Initialize the provider with a provider name and file name.  
     testXmlProvider.Initialize("testProvider", providerAttributes);  
  
     // Call the BuildSiteMap to load the site map information into memory.  
     testXmlProvider.BuildSiteMap();  
  
     // Prints "/myvirtualdirectory/WebForm1.aspx"  
     Response.Write(testXmlProvider.RootNode.Url + "<BR>");  
  
     // Prints "/myvirtualdirectory/WebForm2.aspx"  
     Response.Write(testXmlProvider.CurrentNode.Url + "<BR>");  
 }  
 </SCRIPT>  
```  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="7933b-252">上述程式碼範例會使用位於虛擬根目錄的 ASP.NET 應用程式中的 XML 檔案。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7933b-252">The preceding code example uses an XML file that is located in the virtual root of the ASP.NET application.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="7933b-253">檔案的格式如下：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7933b-253">The file has the following format:</span></span>  
  
```  
<siteMap>  
  <siteMapNode title="RootNode" description="The root page." url="WebForm1.aspx">  
    <siteMapNode title="CurrentNode" description="Some sub page." url="WebForm2.aspx"/>  
  </siteMapNode>  
</siteMap>  
```
